            <title>[WFLY-3765] Runtime modifications in static files of exploded WARs of exploded EARs aren&apos;t reflected.</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-3765</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you put a exploded WAR in $WILDFLY/standalone/deployments/ and modify a static file once the application is deployed and running, such as an HTML or JPEG file, the changes are reflected in the output to the client. However, if the exploded WAR is contained at the same time in a exploded EAR, they aren&apos;t.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
