                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <customfield id="customfield_12310183" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Steps to Reproduce</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>&lt;p&gt;To test it, you can do this in a clean install of Wildfly:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  cd $WILDFLY/standalone/deployments/&lt;br/&gt;
  mkdir -p test.ear/test-war.war/&lt;br/&gt;
  vim test.ear/test-war.war/index.html&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;Write some arbitrary content&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  touch test.ear.dodeploy&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Once it&apos;s deployed, visit the page &quot;index.html&quot; from the Web browser and check that the content is there. Now modify it:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  vim test.ear/test-war.war/index.html&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;Change the content of the file&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you reload the page, it stays with the old content.&lt;/p&gt;</customfieldvalue>

